/login -> authenticates user
/register -> creates new user

/animes?page={i}&order={o} -> list animes available with filtering options
/animes?page={i}&order={o} -> list mangas available with filtering options

/anime/{name} -> returns info about an anime
/manga/{name} -> returns info about a manga

/anime/stream/{name}?episode={i}?chunk={c} -> streams anime video in chunks to client
/anime/stream/{name}?chapter={i}?page={i} -> streams manga page or by photo to client or send it completely

